        <custodhist id="ref4">
            <head>Provenance</head>
            <p>The Albert Harris Photograph Collection was donated to the Abraham Lincoln Brigade Archives by Steve Nelson in 1974. This collection came to New York University in January 2001 as part of the original acquisition of Abraham Lincoln Brigade Archives collections, formerly housed at Brandeis University. The images in the Harris Photograph Collection were separated from the Harris manuscript material at the time of processing.</p>
        </custodhist>
